527
00:23:10,231 --> 00:23:11,571
She's serious. You should calm down.

528
00:23:12,771 --> 00:23:15,811
If you buy sweet fried chicken, you get a butter rice cake for free.

529
00:23:17,341 --> 00:23:19,941
