534
00:23:28,751 --> 00:23:29,920
This is bad.

535
00:23:29,921 --> 00:23:32,291
(Cream shrimp and sweet fried chicken)

536
00:23:33,491 --> 00:23:34,861
Let's pile them up. It'd be better...

537
00:23:35,591 --> 00:23:36,661
